Bosse_Gilgamesh_Status_Confused_Desc: Attacking allies instead of the enemy.
Bosse_Gilgamesh_Status_Minimum_Desc: Shrunk to a fraction of your normal size. Movement speed and damage dealt is reduced while damage taken is increased.
Bosse_Gilgamesh_Status_Toad_Desc: Transformed into a toad and unable to execute actions.
Bosse_Unknown Source_Status_Haste_Desc: Weaponskill cast time and recast time, spell cast time and recast time, and auto-attack delay are reduced.
ContentDesc_Duell auf der großen Brücke: In his quest to acquire the strongest of weapons, the notorious duelist Gilgamesh has long eluded authorities─until now. Forced to take a stand at the impassable Griffin Crossing, he has challenged you to a “duel.” Triumph, and he shall yield his latest prize. But should you fail, your weapons will be forfeit.
instancecontenttextdata_ids_5504_Text: Is just too much for me...
instancecontenttextdata_ids_5507_Text: Ehhh!? Why, I've been had! This is far from the strongest of spears! I feel so betrayed!
instancecontenttextdata_ids_5508_Text: Goodness gracious! I, uh, just remembered something!
instancecontenttextdata_ids_5509_Text: Go on, Enkidu! It's toad─your favorite!
instancecontenttextdata_ids_5510_Text: I must say, I quite enjoy these tussles. I feel we've gained an understanding─
instancecontenttextdata_ids_5511_Text: An understanding that I will pound you silly! Ha ha!
